  "body": "### Problem Description\n\nshap plots should consistently include axes and figsize parameters.\r\n\r\nFor example, \r\n`shap.plots.force(... , figsize=(20, 3), ...)` includes `figsize` but not `ax`.\r\n\r\n`shap.plots.bar( ... )` does not include `figsize` or `ax` parameters.\r\n\r\n`shap.plots.scatter(..., ax=None, ...)` includes `ax` but not `figsize`.\n\n### Alternative Solutions\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional Context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Feature request checklist\n\n- [X] I have checked the issue tracker for duplicate issues.\n- [x] I'd be interested in making a PR to implement this feature",
